I work in global IT, which is the first time I've ever worked in kind of an IT environment. I've always kind of been more on the business side, but now have the

00:03:09.679 --> 00:03:17.600
opportunity to focus more in an IT area where I lead a team of engineers, data scientists, full stack developers, architects, and analysts

00:03:18.039 --> 00:03:22.679
to deliver on a variety of data science and AI projects and initiatives.

